== Amavu n' amavuko ==
'''Hon. Umuhire Adrie''' yavutse taliki 25.07.1977 mu [[Rwanda]], ni umunyapolitiki wo mu Rwanda, senateri watowe mu ntara y'amajyepfo. '''Umuhire Adrie''' afite Impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu inyigisho z'iterambere. 

== Umwuga ==
Guhera mu Kwakira 2019 yabaye umusenateri na perezida wa komite ishinzwe imibereho myiza n'uburenganzira bwa muntu, iyi mirimo aracyayikomeje ('''Senator and the chairperson of the committee on Social Affairs and Human Rights from October 2019- ongoing),''' kuva mu mwaka wa 2006 kugera Ukwakira 2019 yakoze muri kaminuza y'u Rwanda ishami ryigisha ubugeni cg ubuhanzi n'ubumenyi bw'imibereho '''(Assistant Lecturer at University of Rwanda, College of Arts and Social Science from 2006 up to October 2019),''' sibyo gusa kuko kuva 2011 kugera 2016 yabaye umwe mu bagize akanama k'abagore bashinzwe imibereho myiza mu murenge wa Ngoma mu akarere ka Huye, mu intara y' amagepfo ('''A member of National Women Council in Charge of Social Affairs in Ngoma Sector of Huye District /Southern Province: 2011- 2016'''), mu nama y'abasenateri yabaye kuwa 30 Werurwe 2021, umuyobozi wa sena '''Hon Adrie Umuhire''' yavuze ko ubushakashatsi bwabo bwakozwe mu turere 12 muri 30, bugaragaza iterambere ry'ubumwe n'ubwiyunge ko bishoboka niba abaturage bose babishishikarijwe.

